title: U S  stocks higher at close of trade  Dow Jones Industrial Average up 0 61
content:
Investing com   U S  stocks were higher after the close on Wednesday  as gains in the Technology  Industrials and Basic Materials sectors led shares higher

The best performers of the session on the Dow Jones Industrial Average were  Nike  Inc  NYSE NKE   which rose 4 16  or 3 63 points to trade at 90 81 at the close  Meanwhile  Intel Corporation  NASDAQ INTC  added 2 41  or 1 20 points to end at 51 02 and Dow Inc  NYSE DOW  was up 2 32  or 1 08 points to 47 68 in late trade 
The worst performers of the session were UnitedHealth Group Incorporated  NYSE UNH   which fell 1 26  or 2 83 points to trade at 222 17 at the close  Merck   Company Inc  NYSE MRK  declined 0 60  or 0 50 points to end at 83 10 and Procter   Gamble Company  NYSE PG  was down 0 48  or 0 59 points to 123 02
